<map version="1.0.0"><node ID="0AFFD9CE-EF4B-4415-B63D-C2F79DD974E0" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="&#21069;&#31471;&#36335;&#30001;&#30340;&#23454;&#29616;&#26041;&#24335;" COLOR="#164355" POSITION="right" STYLE="bubble"><edge COLOR="#FFFFFF" WIDTH="2" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Light" SIZE="24" /><node ID="E29E37D1-F53A-431E-B243-55327111C118" TEXT="history" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#1286DE" WIDTH="6" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="1DD28AC0-F9C0-4D93-98F8-E9AC1ED87563" TEXT="api" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#1286DE" WIDTH="5" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><node ID="80A10FA1-8B9B-4897-BED5-4AA3B74BED5E" TEXT="window.history.pushState(state, title, url)" COLOR="#344853" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#1286DE" WIDTH="4" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="18" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(184, 14, 61, 1.000000); font: 19px "Courier New"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "CourierNewPSMT"; '>	•	state</span><span style='color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 1.000000); font: 19px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：一个与添加的记录相关联的状态对象，主要用于</span><span style='color: rgba(184, 14, 61, 1.000000); font: 19px "Courier New"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "CourierNewPSMT"; '>popstate</span><span style='color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 1.000000); font: 19px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>事件。该事件触发时，该对象会传入回调函数。也就是说，浏览器会将这个对象序列化以后保留在本地，重新载入这个页面的时候，可以拿到这个对象。如果不需要这个对象，此处可以填</span><span style='color: rgba(184, 14, 61, 1.000000); font: 19px "Courier New"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "CourierNewPSMT"; '>null</span><span style='color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 1.000000); font: 19px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(184, 14, 61, 1.000000); font: 19px "Courier New"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "CourierNewPSMT"; '>	•	title</span><span style='color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 1.000000); font: 19px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：新页面的标题。但是，现在所有浏览器都忽视这个参数，所以这里可以填空字符串。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(184, 14, 61, 1.000000); font: 19px "Courier New"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "CourierNewPSMT"; '>	•	url</span><span style='color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 1.000000); font: 19px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>：新的网址，必须与当前页面处在同一个域。浏览器的地址栏将显示这个网址。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
